[
    {
        "text": "If scientists could create a pill that let you live...",
        "startTime": 3529,
        "endTime": 5914,
        "slowStartTime": 5444,
        "slowEndTime": 9096
    },
    {
        "text": "...twice as long while remaining free of infirmities, would you take it?",
        "startTime": 6021,
        "endTime": 9680,
        "slowStartTime": 9181,
        "slowEndTime": 14745
    },
    {
        "text": "If one considers only the personal benefits that longer life would bring,...",
        "startTime": 10771,
        "endTime": 14537,
        "slowStartTime": 16306,
        "slowEndTime": 22031
    },
    {
        "text": "...the answer might seem like a no-brainer:",
        "startTime": 14901,
        "endTime": 16697,
        "slowStartTime": 22502,
        "slowEndTime": 25271
    },
    {
        "text": "People could spend more quality time with loved ones;",
        "startTime": 17385,
        "endTime": 20056,
        "slowStartTime": 26227,
        "slowEndTime": 30309
    },
    {
        "text": "watch future generations grow up;",
        "startTime": 20360,
        "endTime": 22361,
        "slowStartTime": 30690,
        "slowEndTime": 33766
    },
    {
        "text": "learn new languages;",
        "startTime": 22695,
        "endTime": 23944,
        "slowStartTime": 34192,
        "slowEndTime": 36141
    },
    {
        "text": "master new musical instruments;",
        "startTime": 24264,
        "endTime": 26117,
        "slowStartTime": 36546,
        "slowEndTime": 39400
    },
    {
        "text": "try different careers or travel the world.",
        "startTime": 26453,
        "endTime": 28691,
        "slowStartTime": 39829,
        "slowEndTime": 43261
    },
    {
        "text": "But what about society as a whole?",
        "startTime": 29354,
        "endTime": 31319,
        "slowStartTime": 44181,
        "slowEndTime": 47203
    },
    {
        "text": "Would it be better off if lifespans were doubled?",
        "startTime": 31862,
        "endTime": 34205,
        "slowStartTime": 47943,
        "slowEndTime": 51532
    },
    {
        "text": "A doubled lifespan gives us a chance to recover from our mistakes,...",
        "startTime": 35181,
        "endTime": 38818,
        "slowStartTime": 52921,
        "slowEndTime": 58452
    },
    {
        "text": "...leads us towards longer - term thinking...",
        "startTime": 39395,
        "endTime": 41558,
        "slowStartTime": 59242,
        "slowEndTime": 62562
    },
    {
        "text": "...and reduces health care costs by delaying the onset of expensive diseases of aging.",
        "startTime": 41892,
        "endTime": 46238,
        "slowStartTime": 62988,
        "slowEndTime": 69582
    },
    {
        "text": "It also raises productivity by adding to our prime years.",
        "startTime": 46936,
        "endTime": 50441,
        "slowStartTime": 70554,
        "slowEndTime": 75886
    },
    {
        "text": "Conversely, doubling lifespans won't solve our current social problems.",
        "startTime": 51391,
        "endTime": 55725,
        "slowStartTime": 77236,
        "slowEndTime": 83812
    },
    {
        "text": "War, poverty, etc. may not be helped by having people live longer.",
        "startTime": 56350,
        "endTime": 60675,
        "slowStartTime": 84675,
        "slowEndTime": 91238
    },
    {
        "text": "We must ask, \"What will we get as a society?\"",
        "startTime": 61240,
        "endTime": 64508,
        "slowStartTime": 92010,
        "slowEndTime": 96987
    },
    {
        "text": "Others point out that a doubling of the human lifespan will affect society at every level.",
        "startTime": 65489,
        "endTime": 70100,
        "slowStartTime": 98383,
        "slowEndTime": 105375
    },
    {
        "text": "Notions about marriage, family and work, will change in fundamental ways they say,...",
        "startTime": 70667,
        "endTime": 75403,
        "slowStartTime": 106151,
        "slowEndTime": 113329
    },
    {
        "text": "...as will attitudes toward the young and the old...",
        "startTime": 75759,
        "endTime": 78520,
        "slowStartTime": 113789,
        "slowEndTime": 118005
    },
    {
        "text": "While opinions differ wildly about what the ramifications for society will be...",
        "startTime": 79311,
        "endTime": 83682,
        "slowStartTime": 119116,
        "slowEndTime": 125748
    },
    {
        "text": "...if the human lifespan is extended,...",
        "startTime": 84055,
        "endTime": 86079,
        "slowStartTime": 126233,
        "slowEndTime": 129344
    },
    {
        "text": "...most ethicists agree that the issue should be discussed now,...",
        "startTime": 86588,
        "endTime": 89643,
        "slowStartTime": 130032,
        "slowEndTime": 134690
    },
    {
        "text": "...since it might be impossible to stop or control the technology...",
        "startTime": 90148,
        "endTime": 93476,
        "slowStartTime": 135372,
        "slowEndTime": 140439
    },
    {
        "text": "...once it's developed.",
        "startTime": 93674,
        "endTime": 94851,
        "slowStartTime": 140661,
        "slowEndTime": 142502
    }
]